<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>some.pics (中文)</title><link>https://some.pics</link><description>只是网上的一些图片。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Tue, 12 May 2026 21:21:19 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title>吉他梦</title><link>https://some.pics/6a0399b161da7</link><description>&lt;p&gt;吉他之梦&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Guitar dream" height="3888" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/hiddenflair/6a0399b161da7.jpg" width="5184"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://hiddenflair.some.pics"&gt;@hiddenflair&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 May 2026 21:21:19 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>美好夜散步</title><link>https://some.pics/6a038ad1896a3</link><description>&lt;p&gt;那真是一次愉快的晚间散步。👌🏻&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Dat was nog een lekkere avondwandeling. 👌🏻" height="1486" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/atog/6a038ad1896a3.jpg" width="1179"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://atog.some.pics"&gt;@atog&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 May 2026 20:17:25 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>相似而不同</title><link>https://some.pics/6a0386eaca44c</link><description>&lt;p&gt;相似却不同&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A different crystal glass containing white wine. " height="2000" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/z428/6a0386eaca44c.jpg" width="1126"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://z428.some.pics"&gt;@z428&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 May 2026 20:00:45 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a03817d21b7d</link><description>&lt;p&gt;iPad键盘保护壳上的贴纸。顺时针从上到下：Misfit Stars，又名支持我的亲朋好友[Shannon + Jamie Curtis](shannoncurtis.net)及其音乐。[今天改善点什么](https://improvesomething.today)。我的小网站，本月满10岁。我们都只是漂浮在太空中。没错。[Lex Roman的传奇](https://www.revenuerulebreaker.com)，如果你独立工作或想要独立，可以看看。可爱的图书馆架子。❤️ 我在华盛顿州皮尔斯县投票了。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Stickers on iPad keyboard case thing. Clockwise from top: Misfit Stars AKA supporter of my friends and neighbors [Shannon + Jamie Curtis](shannoncurtis.net) and their music. [Improve Something Today](https://improvesomething.today). My little website, 10 years old this month. We Are All Just Floating in Space. Correct. [Lex Roman’s Legends](https://www.revenuerulebreaker.com), if you work independently or want to, take a look. Cute library shelf. ❤️ I Voted in Pierce County, Washington." height="3352" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/chrkrhc/6a03817d21b7d.jpg" width="4470"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://chrkrhc.some.pics"&gt;@chrkrhc&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 May 2026 19:37:36 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a034e9134a28</link><description>&lt;p&gt;被陷害&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A church tower stands against a grey sky behind a row of apartment blocks. The whole scene is framed by trees in the foreground. The picture is in black and white. " height="3864" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/roteskuffen/6a034e9134a28.jpg" width="2898"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://roteskuffen.some.pics"&gt;@roteskuffen&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 May 2026 16:00:20 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>